snippet.title: Find Inverse and State Domain Restriction
snippet.description:
Learn how to find the inverse of a function and to state the domain restrictions in this free math video tutorial by Mario's Math Tutoring.

0:45 What is the Domain & Range of the Inverse Function

2:16 Summary of How to Find the Inverse and Stating the Domain
